#X text 49 45 We can use the [line~] \, [vline~] and [envgen~] objects to generate a decay only envelope. While [line~]/[vline~] can only be linear \, [envgen~] has different possible curves and exponential settings. The 'lag' curve is a one-pole filter just like you have with [decay~].;
#X obj 317 225 envgen~ -curve lag;
